import React from 'react'
import {
    FormContainer,
    FormWrap,
    FormDisplay,
    FormItems,
    FormLabel,
    FormInput
} from './formElements'


const Form = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <FormContainer>
                <FormWrap>
                    <FormDisplay id="form--contact" >
                        <FormItems>
                            <FormLabel for='name'>Nombre</FormLabel>
                            <FormInput id='name' name='name' required></FormInput>
                        </FormItems>
                    </FormDisplay>
                </FormWrap>
            </FormContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Form
